== Umugambi ==
Amatsinda abiri yabantu atuye mumudugudu umwe, Aloes na Vera. Hariho uguhangana gukabije hagati yabo kwihanganira no kubana kandi buri ruhande rurangwa nibara ryarwo. Iyo abana b'abayobozi b'umujyi ', Aloewin na Veraline, bakundanye bagomba gushaka uburyo bwo guhuza iyo miryango yombi nubwo bangana. Umuganda nyuma uba umwe bitewe nubusabane hagati yabo bombi. 

== Umusaruro ==
Izina ry'iyi filime ryatangajwe mu mwaka wa 2019, hamwe n'itangazo rivuga ko umuyobozi Peter Sedufia yubaka amazu 100 mu rwego rwo gushinga umudugudu wo gufata amashusho mu gace ka Dabala, mu karere ka Volta muri [[Gana]]. Abakinnyi Priscilla Opoku Agyemang, Nana Ama Mcbrown, na Roselyn Ngissah nabo bagaragaye ko bakinnye muri firime.  Worlasi yazanywe no gutanga amajwi ya firime.  Sedufia yavuze ko iyi filime ari "kuzamura umushinga we mbere kandi igamije guha abantu ikintu gifite agaciro n'igihe cyabo." 

''Aloe Vera'' yari ifite ingengo yimari ingana na N58.204.500 ariko yagiye hejuru yingengo yimari N77.606.000 kubera amatariki yo gufata amashusho nyuma yimvura nyinshi yangije ibikoresho byo gufata amashusho.  Imvura kandi yangije cyane firime, Sedufia yavuze ko byagaragaye ko ari ikibazo gikomeye.
